ğŸ“Œ Task 6: Linux Directory Structure
ğŸ”¹ Important Directories
Directory	Purpose
/etc	Configuration files
/var	Variable data
/root	Root user home
/tmp	Temporary files
ğŸ”¹ Temporary directory
cd /tmp

ğŸ”¹ Detailed list
